w:r.w:t: Report on Municipal and communicational expenses of the company of the 2004
According to your request we've prepared a small report which contains information about all
the requested expenses in one form. For obviousness we decided to present them in the form of tables and diagrams.
xpectations the electricity expenses grew up during the winter period, mostly because of heating system.
The telephone charges do not obey any rules, unfortunately, they grew up twice. It is supposed that the reason is a great number of international calls made by management
As you can see, we managed to decrease Internet expenses, particularly because of limitation of bandwidth-time resources and using new smart download policy.
Finally, below is demonstrated the chart of the expenses of the company which shows that the municipal and communicational expenses are less than one third of total expenses.
